data.meta_description: THE PENGUINS OF MADAGASCAR is a trademark of DreamWorks Animation L.L.C.. Filed in September 25 (2009), the THE PENGUINS OF MADAGASCAR covers Paper party decorations; paper party supplies, namely, paper napkins; [, paper place mats, gift wrapping paper and paper gift wrapping ribbons, paper gift wrap bows, paper table cloths and paper party bags; ] children's storybooks, comic books, coloring books, stickers, [ temporary tattoos, pencils, ] all related to an animation television series featuring anthropomorphized penguin characters
